body:
Infinite Enchantments Mod/Lib

Want to play with enchantments more than 255?
Enchantments look like this `Sharpness enchantment.level.255`?

This mod/lib has fixed all that for you!
Enchantments now made to maximum 255 -> 1000000000 (1 billion!)
`Sharpness enchantment.level.255` made `Sharpness 255`

How to install 
For Players :
1. Download the jar file
2. Put it in the `.minecraft/versions/<Neoforge version name>/mods`

Now you can enchant the item with commands

REMEMBER : Using enchantments like fortune with high levels can cause many drops to drop, causing the game to crash 

For Modders:
1. Put the following in `build.gradle` 
```
repositories {
    exclusiveContent {
        forRepository {
            maven {
                url "https://cursemaven.com"
            }
        }
        filter {
            includeGroup "curse.maven"
        }
    }
}
```
2. Put the cursemaven snippet in `dependencies` in `build.gradle`
3. Reload gradle changes to implement it

Now modders can `ItemStack#set` the `Enchantment` with `DataComponents.ENCHANTMENT` and `ItemEnchantments` like follows

```
public static void setOverleveledEnchant(ItemStack stack, Holder<Enchantment> enchantment, int level) {
        ItemEnchantments existing = stack.getOrDefault(DataComponents.ENCHANTMENTS, ItemEnchantments.EMPTY);
        ItemEnchantments.Mutable mutable = new ItemEnchantments.Mutable(existing);
        mutable.set(enchantment, level);
        stack.set(DataComponents.ENCHANTMENTS, mutable.toImmutable());
    }
```

REMEMBER : The "max_level" field in any `<enchantment_name>.json` still needs to be a lower value like 5, as the value determines the number of books generated in the creative mode tab (that means setting it to suppose 1 billion will create 1 billion books, and the game crashes)

Drop any suggestions for updates in the comments!
